data.description: Absolutely Stunning Home with remodeled features and upgrades you will love!  This is an exceptional one story floorplan with a huge living and dining room, with a separate den and open concept kitchen.  The home is loaded with upgrades such as stainless steel appliances, including gas range, dishwasher, fridge and microwave, granite countertops, and a convenient kitchen island.  The floors are all updated with vinyl plank flooring for easy maintenance.  The bedrooms offer spacious rooms for each member, with nicely sized closets.  The master suite offers a splendid retreat, with huge walk-in closets, and a full private bathroom.  All bathrooms have solid surface counters and have updated fixtures and finishes.  The private backyard offers a drive around driveway with a gate on each side, perfect for parking and privacy, and there's a covered back porch for enjoying the outdoors, and a wonderful deck perfect for barbecues and entertaining!   This home offers all new everything in 2019, including an architectural shingle roof, new lighting and plumbing fixtures, new HVAC, new flooring and more!  Just go ahead and buy it today before it is gone!
